== Deng Local a Maliliari ampong Apupuntalan ==

Dakal la reng bageng managiag kareng tau king lugal, kayabe la reng bebe dayatmalat a maki maputing balas king mauli ning [[Tyre, Lebanon|Tyre]], ampo ing pamag-snorkle o pamanyisid kareng makalbug a ruina o mengalasak a lakanbalen/ciudad malapit kareng mangatuang lakanbalen ning [[Sidon]] ampong [[Tyre, Lebanon|Tyre]]. Aburi do reng mahilig king cultura deng dakal taung Pazar a kanita pang panaun a Ottoman, at makapag-relax ka kaibat ning patingapun king metung a ''seafood restaurant'' nung nu me ababation king lalam ing dayatmalat a Mediterraneo. Mararapat murin king [[Mauling Lebanon]] ing fiestang [[Tyre, Lebanon|Tyre]] o Tyre festival, nung nu libu-libu lang turista deng daratang banua-banua.

== Relihiun king South Governorate ==

Shia la reng keraklan, 45.9%;
Sunni la reng kadua, 37%;
Cristianu la reng katlu, 17%;
Druze la reng tauli, 0.1%.

